==English==

===Verb===
{{head|en|verb}}

# {{lb|en|idiomatic|US}} To attempt to stay [[cheerful]] in a [[dire]] situation; to [[proceed]] with a task, [[ignore|ignoring]] an upcoming [[hazard]], hoping for a good outcome.
# {{lb|en|idiomatic|US}} To enter a situation with little or no [[understanding]] of the possible [[consequences]].

